RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT MODULE_ID, MODULE_DESC FROM OLVWS_MODULES WHERE CH_CLASS_APPLICABLE = 'Y' AND ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY MODULE_ID
SELECT* FROM (SELECT PARTY_TYPE FROM OLTMS_PARTY_TYPE_CLASS A WHERE A.MODULE = ? ORDER BY PARTY_TYPE) WHERE 1= 1
SELECT EVENT_CODE,EVENT_DESCR FROM OLTBS_EVENT WHERE MODULE = ? AND ALLOW_ASSOCIATION_OF_CHARGE = 'Y' ORDER BY EVENT_CODE
SELECT EVENT_CODE,EVENT_DESCR FROM OLTBS_EVENT WHERE MODULE = ? AND ALLOW_APPLICATION_OF_CHARGE = 'Y' ORDER BY EVENT_CODE
SELECT EVENT_CODE,EVENT_DESCR FROM OLTBS_EVENT WHERE MODULE = ? AND ALLOW_LIQUIDATION_OF_CHARGE = 'Y' ORDER BY EVENT_CODE
SELECT AMOUNT_TAG,DESCRIPTION FROM OLTBS_AMOUNT_TAG WHERE MODULE = ? AND CHARGE_ALLOWED ='Y' AND LANGUAGE_CODE = GLOBAL.LANG ORDER BY AMOUNT_TAG
SELECT RULE_ID,DESCRIPTION FROM LFTB_ICCF_RLAVL WHERE RULE_TYPE='H' AND RECORD_STAT ='O' AND ONCE_AUTH ='Y' ORDER BY RULE_ID
SELECT CCY_CODE, CCY_NAME FROM CYTMS_CCY_DEFN WHERE ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' ORDER BY CCY_CODE
SELECT DISTINCT A.CLASS_CODE,A.MODULE FROM CSTM_ROLE_TO_HEAD_CLASS A,OLTM_CLASS B WHERE A.MODULE =? AND A.CLASS_CODE=B.CLASS_CODE AND B.AUTH_STAT='A' AND B.RECORD_STAT='O'
SELECT CLASS_CODE FROM OLTM_CLASS WHERE MODULE=? AND ONCE_AUTH = 'Y' AND RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND CLASS_TYPE = 'AC'
SELECT MIS_GROUP FROM MITM_MIS_GROUP WHERE ONCE_AUTH='Y'

RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: CURRENCY = 'ALL' AND CURRENCY2 = 'ALL' AND CUSTOMER = 'ALL' AND CUST_GROUP='ALL' AND BRANCH='ALL' AND TYPE = 'H'
